---
title: Ginger Beef Stir-Fry with Snappy Asparagus
description: A HelloFresh classic! Tender beef and crisp, springy asparagus are quickly stir-fried with warming ginger and served over fluffy basmati rice. Hoisin sauce adds a touch of sweetness and an incredible umami depth. It’s so sweet and succulent, we’re sure you’ll agree with us that this is a recipe worth visiting again and again.
